race.comment: MOFEED (2) is a consistent conveyance who has hit the top-four at his past nine starts and strikes a very winnable contest here. Rates the testing material against this line-up. DUSAN (1) loves it here around this circuit with two wins and a placing from just three spins. Gets some weight relief with the 3kg claim and looms as the main danger. MISS MOLOKAI (5) has been right there in six of her past seven starts and will be rock-hard fit for this. Top-three candidate on best form. BOWDARCIE (6) has placed over this course and distance and will get a soft run in transit from gate two. In the mix for some minor money.
